There are some bugs to the map... And there is a secret teleport, also the teleporters are a little bit messed up so if you go at the same time you might get stuck.

I will fix all of these bugs with the next version of this map.

------NOTES----------
This is an awp map so there are several intentional glitches such as the houses have lifted walls for better awping capabilities.. THESE ARE NOT ACCIDENTAL.
